snippet.title: How 'The Most Hated Actress' Destroyed Her Own Career || GC
snippet.description:
This video is about Johnny Depp and his ex, Amber Heard. Amber destroyed Johnny's career when she filed for a divorce in 2016. But what she doesn't know is that she got exposed a lot for lying and now has a lot of hate to deal with.

Like, subscribe, and enjoy!

My gaming channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvS_GGxma3IJDovx9psdn_g

Petitions:

Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2: https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

Keep Johnny Depp as Grindelwald: https://www.change.org/p/warner-brothers-keep-johnny-depp-as-grindelwald

To Get Johnny Depp's Career Back: https://www.change.org/p/johnny-s-fans-to-get-johnny-depp-s-career-back

Give Johnny Depp His Roles Back: https://www.change.org/p/warner-brothers-give-johnny-deep-his-roles-back

Justice For Johnny Depp: https://www.change.org/p/justice-for-johnny-depp

We Want Johnny Depp Back as Captain Jack Sparrow: https://www.change.org/p/the-walt-disney-company-we-want-johnny-depp-back-as-captain-jack-sparrow-65c54dc0-db49-47ff-bcb0-726fcf1cb81a
